{
  "texts": [
    "Traditional farming methods alone will struggle to achieve this.",
    "Agritech, which involves deploying technology, innovations, and scientific thinking in agriculture to enhance productivity, is part of the solution for scaling up food production sustainably.",
    "Agriculture has undergone significant changes and improvements thanks to new technologies.",
    "Smart technologies, including artificial intelligence, robotics, and the Internet of Things, play a crucial role in achieving enhanced productivity.",
    "The agritech industry utilizes the Internet of Things and other technologies to address the challenges of feeding a growing global population (Rialti et al. 2022)."
  ]
}